    Headphone

    The essence of a song is felt best when you listen to it on a good medium. You can easily find the best earphones while browsing through the plethora of options available online. From entry-level options to audiophile-level models, find devices that will suit your budget and your taste. Take your audio production career to the next level by choosing studio-quality headphones. Find earphones in a varied range of colours and designs, enabling you to choose a device that suits your style. Select the traditional canal phone or pick models with ear tips and ear wings. You can even find behind-the-neck headsets that are sweat-proof and water-resistant, making them the ideal choice for morning walks and workout sessions. Travel with foldable and collapsible headsets that would easily fit inside your bag, thus saving you the inconvenience of always wearing the device. Avoid the hassle of tangled wires by choosing true wireless earbuds that can be connected to any device using Bluetooth. Find plenty of headsets that are compatible with various devices, including audio players, TVs, tablets, gaming consoles, etc. Browse through brands like boAt, Mivi, OnePlus, Sony, JBL, and many more to find the best earphones for yourself.

    Buy Headphones Online - Don’t Stop Grooving 

    It isn’t always possible to enjoy your music using speakers, and that’s where a good pair of headphones can come in handy. Headphones not only let you listen to your favorite form of music peacefully, but they also help you shut yourself away from the things that bother you. Today, there are so many different types of headphones and a hundred or more brands to choose from. But, to ensure that you are putting your money on the right set of headphones, it is of key importance that you learn a little something about some of the common headset types and the popular brands that manufacture them. Here’s what you need to know: 

    Phone headphones are the go-to option for music lovers and smartphone gamers. A pair of headphones is what an audiophile needs while travelling long distances or concentrating on a particular task. If you’re a gamer, find headphones that will give you clear and crisp sound to win at your favourite game. People prefer to use headphones to consume their favourite audio or video content anytime and anywhere. Select from the varied range of over the ear, in the ear, and wireless headphones available online. Use Bluetooth to seamlessly connect your phone to a wireless headphone or a wired 3.5 mm jack to listen to your favourite audio. Select sweat proof or waterproof headphones to use during your usual morning walks. Browse through the collection of foldable over the head headphones available online that can easily be stored in your backpack while travelling. Explore headphones with good-quality microphones to record voice or have an uninterrupted conversation over a voice call. Find behind the neck Bluetooth headphones with convenient in-line control and a long-lasting battery. Check and compare headphone prices and features online and find a headset that suits your needs. Get phone headphones from brands like boAt, Samsung, Apple, Mivi, Sony, etc. 

    Enjoy Songs, Podcasts, and More with the OnePlus Bullets Wireless Z 

    One of the most important accessories today is a pair of earphones. It not only helps you listen to audio content without bothering others, but also lets you attend calls easily, especially when your hands are busy. A great example of one such headset is the OnePlus Bullets Wireless Z. Not only are these earphones pretty great to look at, but they also tick all the boxes when it comes to their performance-related features. One of the factors that separates this headset from ordinary wired ones is its wireless design, which makes it highly convenient for one to carry around everywhere. Do the OnePlus Bullets Wireless Z in-ear buds already have your interest? Here a few other facts about them that you should know to understand why they are they real deal when it comes to wireless earphones:
    Lightweight
    If you are used to wearing your earphones around your neck all day, then you wouldn’t want them to weigh you down - would you? That’s where these OnePlus earphones are game-changing. With a weight of about 28 g, these earbuds are comfortable, offer a snug fit, and they feel as light as a fly. You can enjoy all your playlists or even indulge in podcasts that are several hours long without feeling any discomfort.
    Battery
    Ordinary earphones are notorious for not offering enough battery life, but that’s not the case with these bad boys from OnePlus. Rocking a powerful battery, these earbuds deliver a whopping battery life of about 20 hours on a single full charge. Now, that’s quite a lot of juice to exhaust - isn’t it? But, let’s assume you somehow managed to exhaust the battery of these earphones. You can still get them up and running in about 10 minutes of time - yes, that's how long it takes for these earbuds to offer up to 10 hours of battery life. 
    Connectivity
    With the jacks out of the equation, these earphones are all the more easy to connect to your smartphone or any other Bluetooth playback device. These earbuds support Bluetooth 5.0, and you won’t have to worry about the hassle of going through a set-up process. Pairing these babies is as simple as separating the earbuds and then tapping on “Connect”. Now, is that magic or what?
    IP55 Rating
    Travelling for long hours or working out at the gym can cause you to sweat profusely, isn’t it? In cases like these, an ordinary headset would probably give up, but not the OnePlus Bullets Wireless Z. These earphones boast an IP55 rating, which makes them dust- and sweat-resistant, to ensure that you don’t get the heebie-jeebies every time you use them to listen to music when you are sweating from a workout or you are outdoors.
    If these features are what you’re looking for in a wireless headset, go online and order a pair of OnePlus Bullets Wireless Z earphones.


    Types of Earphones
     

    Wireless  Headphones

    Just like the traditional wired headphones, there are wireless headphones that are available online. But, what separates wireless earbuds from the wired ones is how convenient and hassle-free they are as compared to wired headsets. With these headsets, you don’t have to worry about ensuring that their wires don’t get damaged. That’s because these headphones connect to your phone/tablet or any other compatible smart device using Bluetooth and radio frequencies, among other options. This feature not only helps you indulge in high-quality audio, but it also saves you the trouble of untangling the wires every time you wish to listen to good music. You can easily find some great-quality radio frequency headphones or Bluetooth headphones on online stores.  

    Sports Headphones 
    When was the last time that you went to the gym for a workout and your earphones stayed put in your ears? Never, right? You’re probably starting to think, “How do I ensure that my headphones stay in place even during complex movements?” Aren’t you? Well, you certainly need to try sports earphones. These babies not only offer a snug fit to ensure that you’re pumped up throughout your workout sessions, but they are also sweat-resistant so that their performance isn’t affected by it.   
     
    Travel  Headphones
    Go to anyone who travels frequently and ask him/her, “What’s the one piece of advice that you have for an aspiring traveller?’ And, 9 out of 10 times, that person will probably tell you to travel light. Yep, there’s barely anyone who likes dealing with excess baggage weight, especially if it’s in the form of your favorite headphones. And, travel headphones were invented to help people overcome such problems. These headsets aren’t just lightweight, they are easy to pack too. Slide them in your backpack or wear them around your neck - travel headphones won’t be a burden. 
     
    Extra Bass  Headphones
    Not everyone has an ear for music that has powerful lows. But, if you are a glutton for that kind of music, then extra-bass headphones are something that you really need to consider before making a buying decision. Brands such as Sony are famous for manufacturing this type of headphones. Basically, what these headphones do is digitally increase the low-frequency sounds in the audio that you’re listening to and then maximize it to offer you a punchy sound that every bass lover longs to hear.  
      
    Noise-canceling Headphones  
      
    Be it dealing with a bunch of people who just won’t keep quiet or with the annoying noise coming from your neighborhood, situations like these can be quite annoying. But, let me tell you this - you won’t have to deal with such situations if you had a pair of noise-cancellation headphones. Noise-canceling headsets, in general, reduce/eliminate unwanted ambient sounds, and they do so by using active noise control. This helps you enjoy audio content in great quality without even having to raise the volume significantly. Another great thing about these headsets is that they increase the signal-to-noise ratio when you are in an aviation environment, ensuring that you don’t miss out on important announcements. How cool is that?  
     
    Now that you are aware of some of the types of headphones that are available in the market today, it would only be fair if we shared the name of some reliable brands that you can consider, right? Well, in that case, you can always go for brands, such as Flipkart Smartbuy, Mi, Bose, JBL, Sennheiser, Skullcandy, Audio Technica, and Sony, among other options. But remember, although these brands make some really cool headphones, they are not the only options that you have. By searching online, you can find hundreds of other headphone manufacturers that make equally good headphones.

    Question and Answers

    1. Q.Do headphones work with Redmi Note Pro?
      A.Yes, They get along hassle-free with all types of mobiles, tablets, laptops, and other devices.
    2. Q.Can I use headphones during my Zoom meetings?
      A.Yes, It is the best choice of equipment while taking calls, playing games, attending Zoom meetings, and being in online classes.
    3. Q.I have big ears. Will earphones with a mic suit me?
      A.Yes, They suit people of different ages and ear types equally well without any hassle.
    4. Q.Do earphones feel heavy while they are on and in long-term use?
      A.No, Earbuds are very comfortable to wear, offer you a snug fit, and feel almost weightless. You can wear them for long hours without any discomfort.
    5. Q.Is there any other earphone option except for the head style?
      A.Yes, You can choose from various styles in earphones, like behind the neck, canal phone, ear clip, earbud, or over the head. Browse online and find the ones that best suit your needs.
    6. Q.Are earphones with mic sweat proof and water resistant?
      A.Some earphone models have sweat proof and water resistance features to give you the best experience while walking, jogging, and other doing outdoor activities. You can read the product description to be sure about these features before your purchase.
    7. Q.What brands offer good high-quality headphones?
      A.Various brands like BoAt, OnePlus, Realme, Boult Audio, Sony, JBL, and many more offer a wide range of earphones online. You can scroll through different models, compare them, and select the ones that suit you best from the comfort of your home.
    8. Q.Are all the headphones in the ear type?
      A.No, They come in different types like in the ear, on the ear, and true wireless. You can choose the ones that meet your needs and requirements.
    9. Q.Can I use earphones with a mic while playing games like PUBG and free fire?
      A.Yes, You can use them while playing games to take your gaming experience to another level.
    10. Q.How is the quality of earphones in traffic?
      A.They block out outside noise and allow you to get immersed in full audio and video experience. You can hear your favourite soundtracks loud and clear.
